Malba with Play2.3 sample project
=================================

* Get source code from github
```bash
$ git clone git@github.com:Shanon/Malba.git
```

* Publish Malba-client-playPlugin into your local
```bash
$ cd Malba
$ activator malba-client-playPlugin/publish-local
```

* Run sample project
```bash
$ cd sample/play2.3
$ activator run
```

* Access to `http://localhost:9000/`
